description: One of the greatest childhood memories you can have is when the ice cream truck stops right in front of your house and you can load up on all your favorite frozen treats. In that theme, Just Chillin is bringing ice cream to the streets of Orange County... and to you! Now, instead of waiting for the clarion call of the ice cream tune, you can bring the truck right to you! Why wait?
name: Just Chill N Ice Cream Truck
